snippet.title: BMo
snippet.description:
Here you will learn game design and development from a multitude of unity tutorials!

I used to spend all of my time making games, but now work full time as a software engineer doing other cool things. 

Fortunately, I use the little free time I have to spread the knowledge I've accumulated over the years!

And I do it all because I love you.
